Step1 : https://apps.twitter.com/  -> Create New App 
Step2 : Get Consumer Key (API Key), Consumer Secret (API Secret), Access Token, Access Token Secret
Step3 : Create Flume configuration file with the above keys specified
Step4 : put the config file in /home/remya (local path in the remote machine)
Step5 : Execute this command in the command line
	flume-ng agent --conf conf --conf-file flume_remya.conf --name TwitterAgent
